WEBVTT

00:04:58.800 --> 00:05:03.000
he has seen the highs and lows of life,
has risen and fallen.

00:05:03.000 --> 00:05:07.880
You get all these things with age,

00:05:07.880 --> 00:05:11.940
so my character is not large and muscular 
like those in Western comics,

00:05:11.940 --> 00:05:13.800
but he is intelligent from experience.

00:05:13.800 --> 00:05:17.320
That is why I created Chacha Chaudhary.

00:05:17.320 --> 00:05:20.320
(Applause)

00:05:21.160 --> 00:05:23.520
Let me give you my own example.

00:05:23.520 --> 00:05:27.240
I did this project when I was around 25.

00:05:27.240 --> 00:05:33.480
I met around four to five hundred people